      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between refined performance and everyday practicality. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, accented by well-preserved trim and alloy wheels that show only minor signs of careful use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the premium upholstery remains supple, and every electronic feature\u2014from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, benefiting from a consistent maintenance schedule and recent fluid changes. The transmission shifts seamlessly, providing a confident and engaging driving experience. Whether you\u2019re commuting through the city or embarking on a weekend getaway, this car offers reliability and style. It has been smoke-free, garage-kept, and is ready for its next owner to drive away today.",
      "price": 34800.0,
